cardenas 24 perched on one of the simple cementcovered graves 
painted pink blue and white and overrun with weeds and dust from 
unpaved streets 
cardenas had also gone to new york but was deported last year 
as an illegal alien 
leaving here for new york is a change of life for the better 
because there is nothing here he said as marquezs funeral 
procession arrived 
you stay here and do this he said pointing to a ragclad 
grave digger or you go to new york 
