destruction and creation 
people who live here are emotionally prepared for it but you 
still hope its not going to happen said donna olson whose home 
was destroyed in the 1986 flow she lives with her three children 
in a rented house threatened by the flow 
i feel very emotional about this but i also know theres a 
balance to pele i know everything here has been born from the 
lava its a circle 
