24 billion below the level bush wants 
it rejects the 55 billion in cuts bush has requested in 
medicare aid to the elderly and handicapped it boosts federal 
welfare programs by 53 billion and adds 4 billion to the 45 
billion bush is seeking for education and job training programs 
