37425 this morning down from 37505 bid late tuesday 
in zurich the bid price was 37440 from 37600 late tuesday 
gold in hong kong rose 340 an ounce today to close at 37534 
silver dropped in london to a bid price of 501 a troy ounce 
from tuesdays 502 per ounce 
