co announced its own magic summer promotion 
cocacola is distributing 750000 cans of what appear to be 
regular cans of its flagship cocacola classic but actually 
contain prizes 
each specially designed can contains a mechanism that will 
spring up when the top is pulled and deliver up to 200 in cash or 
a certificate for other prizes 
the cans are designed so that the spring mechanism and the prize 
stay dry because they are separated by a barrier from liquid in the 
can bottom 
