on behalf of public officials 
the resolution trust corp action was announced wednesday in 
response to policy directives in the sampl bailout legislation 
enacted by congress last summer 
the rtc action also calls for establishment of a special 
committee which will conduct formal reviews when rtc employes 
believe they have received inappropriate requests from public 
officials 
it also outlined procedures for meetings between rtc employes 
public officials and their constituents including a requirement 
that such meetings be attended by two or more rtc employees one of 
whom must be a seniorlevel employee 
</TEXT>
